{:cell/id "numeracy"
 :cell/glyph "数"
 :cell/kind :langgraph
 :cell/runtime :wasm
 :cell/entry "py/agent.py"
 :cell/handler "handle_numeracy"
 :cell/doc "Counting → arithmetic → fractions → algebra → calculus path. Learner discovers through guided hands-on (G13 inquiry-first). Content on IPFS (G1). Anti-addiction UX (G3). Minor attestations aggregate (G6)."
